OL,3,CLondon-born teen to become first
OL,4,CCatholic millennial saint
OL,6,FA London-born teenager will become the
OL,7,FCatholic Church's first millenial
OL,8,Fsaint, after his cause for
OL,9,Fcanonisation was approved by church
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FCarlo Acutis, who died from leukemia
OL,13,Fin 2006 at the age of 15, was renowned
OL,14,Ffor using his computing skills to
OL,15,Fspread awareness of the Catholic faith
OL,16,Fand earned the nickname "God's
OL,17,Finfluencer".
