OL,4,CCatholic millennial saint
OL,6,FBeing recognised as a saint in the
OL,7,FCatholic Church can take decades, but
OL,8,Fthe cause of Acutis has moved swiftly,
OL,9,Fwith the teenager developing a devoted
OL,10,Ffollowing across the world.
OL,12,FHis story has been seen to better
OL,13,Fconnect the Catholic Church with
OL,14,Fyounger generations in a digital age.
OL,16,FThe church's sainthood process usually
OL,17,Frequires two miracles attributed to
OL,18,Fthe candidate.
