OL,4,CCatholic millennial saint
OL,6,FAcutis was beatified and declared
OL,7,F"blessed" in 2020 after his first
OL,8,Fmiracle, when he reportedly healed a
OL,9,FBrazilian boy who touched one of
OL,10,FAcutis' T-shirts, before making a
OL,11,Fmiraculous recovery from a rare
OL,12,Fpancreatic disorder.
OL,14,FThe Pope later verified Acutis was the
OL,15,Fsource of this miracle.
