OL,6,FThe second miracle attributed to
OL,7,FAcutis relates to the reported healing
OL,8,Fof a girl from Costa Rica who had
OL,9,Fsuffered a head trauma after falling
OL,10,Ffrom her bicycle in Florence, Italy,
OL,11,Fwhere she was studying.
OL,13,FHer mother said she prayed for her
OL,14,Fdaughter's recovery at the tomb of
OL,15,FAcutis in Assisi.
