OL,6,FThat left one final step, completed
OL,7,Ftoday, when the Vatican announced the
OL,8,Fpope had decreed the canonisation
OL,9,Fwould go ahead, after cardinals,
OL,10,Fconvened by the pope, voted in favour
OL,11,Fof Acutis' sainthood.
OL,13,FThat canonisation ceremony, expected
OL,14,Fto take place in St Peter's Square, in
OL,15,FVatican City, will be the moment where
OL,16,FAcutis is formally declared a saint -
OL,17,Fmeaning the Catholic Church across the
OL,18,Fworld can name parishes and schools
OL,19,Fafter the teenager, and will remember
OL,20,Fhim annually on a "feast day".
