OL,3,CLondon-born teen to become first
OL,4,CCatholic millennial saint
OL,6,FAcutis, who was born in London, in
OL,7,F1991 - putting him squarely in the
OL,8,Fmillennial generation cohort - is
OL,9,Fremembered by friends and family as
OL,10,Fenjoying playing the saxophone,
OL,11,Ffootball and video games.
OL,13,FHis mother, Antonia Salzano, described
OL,14,Fher son as a "sign of hope" who shows
OL,15,Fthat holiness is possible today.
OL,17,FMs Salzano added that from the age of
OL,18,Fnine, the youngster spent time helping
OL,19,Fthe homeless in Milan and giving his
OL,20,Fpocket money to those sleeping on the
OL,21,Fstreets.
